What you need to know:

Juventus, with their nine-year reign ended, and AC Milan, whose title pursuit fizzled out following a considerable downturn in 2021, find themselves fighting to secure a place in the Champions League.Lille are three wins from a first French title since 2011, and fourth overall. Of their three remaining games, the clash against neighbouring Lens appears the most testing.Julian Nagelsmann will take over at Bayern next season, but the job isn't quite finished yet for outgoing coach Hansi Flick in Bavaria.